    "rich_text_A7bE3a": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_e4LJYq": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "650g Recycled Cotton Gabardine",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_JbjHCQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Chosen for weight, density and presence — not lightness.<br/>Sourced in Italy, from a mill with over fifty years of experience.<br/>The dense weave gives structure and clarity. It holds its shape. It stays comfortable.<br/>Each piece is garment-dyed in Vicenza. Subtle variations emerge along seams and edges. No two are exactly the same.<br/>Garment dyeing softens the fabric, removing tension.<br/>When a garment is meant to last, the fabric must carry substance as well as character.</p>"
